Town of Iota Prop No. 1 -- 5 Mills - M&BOA - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Town of Iota Propositions
Proposition No. 1
(Tax Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall the Town of lota, State of Louisiana, (the "Town") under the provisions of Article VI, Section 22, Section 27(B), Section 30(A) of the Constitution of the State of Louisiana of 1974, levy and collect a Five (5) Mills Tax ("Renewal") on all property subject to taxation situated in said Town (current estimated annual amount of $21,300.00), annually for a period of ten (10) years, commencing with the year 2015 and ending in the year 2024, for the purpose of constructing and maintaining streets, roads, highways and avenues within the said Town?

Race.SpecificTitle: Town of Iota Prop No. 2 -- 5 Mills - M&BOA - 10 Yrs.
Race.SummaryText:
Town of Iota Propositions
Proposition No. 2
(Tax Renewal)
Race.FullText: Shall the Town of lota, State of Louisiana, (the "Town") under the provisions of Article VI, Section 22, Section 27(B), Section 30(A) of the Constitution of the State of Louisiana of 1974, levy and collect a Five (5) Mills Tax ("Renewal") on all property subject to taxation situated in said Town (current estimated annual amount of $21,300.00), annually for a period of ten (10) years, commencing with the year 2015 and ending in the year 2024, for the purpose of maintaining public buildings, improving and maintaining bridges and the drainage system of the said Town?
